description: Detroit's Mac Shack is specializing in creative mac n cheese, featuring items like the Koh San Road, Cheech's Trip, Dune Climber, Vegan or create your own. Also available are garlic fries and poutine! With the belief that lovingly prepared food warms the soul and brings people together, Mac Shack uses fresh, high quality ingredients in all of the recipes to create the ultimate street food experience.
name: Mac Shack
